rt's Students - Pre"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID10","SecondaryAttribute":"Dear ${q:\/\/QID22\/ChoiceTextEntryValue\/1}, \u00a0 Please read the following instructions carefully.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Dear ${q:\/\/QID22\/ChoiceTextEntryValue\/1},\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>Please read the following instructions carefully.<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"T","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Dear ${q:\/\/QID22\/ChoiceTextEntryValue\/1}, \u00a0 Please read the following instructions carefully.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID10","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID12","SecondaryAttribute":"In this game, you will play the role of an investor making repeated investment decisions. \u00a0 Each...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div>In this game, you will play the role of an investor making repeated investment decisions.<\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>Each round, you will see three different companies and their four characteristics:<\/div>\n<br>\n<img src=\"https:\/\/insead.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_02pSOhwr8tvnZIx\" style=\"width: 500px; height: 135px;\">\n<ul>\n\t<li><strong>Company Valuation:<\/strong> The current value of the company, in dollars (between $500,000 and $3,000,000).<\/li>\n\t<li><strong>Sector of Activity:&nbsp;<\/strong>The core business of the company (Electronics, Robotics, or Biotechnology).<\/li>\n\t<li><strong>Market Size:&nbsp;<\/strong>The number of customers who could be interested in the product that the company is selling (between 2000 and 14,000).<\/li>\n\t<li><strong>Number of Competitors:&nbsp;<\/strong>The number of competitors that the company currently has (between 2 and 14).<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<br>\nYou will choose, each round, one company in which to invest <strong>$100,000<\/strong> in.<br>\n&nbsp;","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"T","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"In this game, you will play the role of an investor making repeated investment decisions. \u00a0 Each...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID12"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID13","SecondaryAttribute":"Click to write the question text","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Click to write the question text","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"T","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Click to write the question text","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID13"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID20","SecondaryAttribute":"After playing 20 rounds, the game will end. We will also show you several pairs of companies, and...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div>\n<div><strong>After playing 20 rounds, the game will end. <\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div><br>\n<strong>We will also show you several pairs of companies, and you will have to predict which of the two would give you the larger Return on Investment. <\/strong><\/div>\n\n<div><br>\nYou will then be asked to answer a short survey. We will debrief the simulation in class.<\/div>\n\n<div><br>\n<span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c;\"><strong>This is an individual exercise: Do not discuss your strategies and results with anyone.<\/strong><\/span><\/span><\/div>\n\n<div><br>\n&nbsp;<\/div>\n<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"T","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"After playing 20 rounds, the game will end. We will also show you several pairs of companies, and...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID20"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID22","SecondaryAttribute":"Please enter your first and last name:","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Please enter your first and last name:","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"Info","QuestionID":"QID22","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"FORM","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText","AllowFreeResponse":"false"},"QuestionDescription":"Please enter your first and last name:","Choices":{"1":{"Display":"First Name","InputHeight":29,"InputWidth":240,"TextEntry":"on"},"2":{"Display":"Last Name","InputHeight":29,"InputWidth":240,"TextEntry":"on"}},"ChoiceOrder":["1","2"],"Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":null}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID23","SecondaryAttribute":"Dear participant, \u00a0 Please read the following instructions carefully.","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Dear participant,<br><div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>Please read the following instructions carefully.<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"T","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"Dear participant, \u00a0 Please read the following instructions carefully.","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"QuestionID":"QID23"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID24","SecondaryAttribute":"After you made your decision, we will reveal the Return On Investment (ROI) that you earned from...","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"<div>After you made your decision, we will reveal the Return On Investment (ROI) that you earned from the company.<br>\n<br>\n<img style=\"width: 300px; height: 119px;\" src=\"https:\/\/insead.eu.qualtrics.com\/CP\/Graphic.php?IM=IM_9GrdMrqYJnLbazX\"><\/div>\n\n<div>\n<div><em>&nbsp;<\/em><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<div><em><strong>Your goal is to learn how the characteristic(s) of the companies relate to the ROIs that you get. <\/strong><\/em><\/div>\n\n<div>&nbsp;<\/div>\n\n<div>\n<div><em><strong>Learning this might not be easy, for four reasons:<\/strong><\/em><\/div>\n\n<ul>\n\t<li>The task is <strong>complex<\/strong>: There are many different variables<\/li>\n\t<li>The ROIs may be <strong>volatile<\/strong>, and change over time<\/li>\n\t<li>The relationship between attributes and ROIs is <strong>ambiguous<\/strong>:<strong> <\/strong>It is unclear which attribute(s), if any, predict larger ROIs<\/li>\n\t<li>There is <strong>uncertainty<\/strong>: The ROIs might be influenced by other factors than the characteristics you observe<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/div>","DefaultChoices":false,"DataExportTag":"T","QuestionID":"QID24","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"QuestionDescription":"After you made your decision, we will reveal the Return On Investment (ROI) that you earned from...","ChoiceOrder":[],"Validation":{"Settings":{"Type":"None"}},"GradingData":[],"Language":[],"NextChoiceId":4,"NextAnswerId":1,"DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false}}},{"SurveyID":"SV_4ZrvZcuZLcwo2JU","Element":"STAT","PrimaryAttribute":"Survey Statistics","SecondaryAttribute":null,"TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"MobileCompatible":false,"ID":"Survey Statistics"}}]}